	(290,'_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51','<div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.org/news/2014/05/wordpress-3-9-1/\'>WordPress 3.9.1 Maintenance Release</a> <span class=\"rss-date\">8 maj, 2014</span><div class=\"rssSummary\">After three weeks and more than 9 million downloads of WordPress 3.9, we’re pleased to announce that WordPress 3.9.1 is now available. This maintenance release fixes 34 bugs in 3.9, including numerous fixes for multisite networks, customizing widgets while previewing themes, and the updated visual editor. We’ve also made some improvements to the new audio/vi</div></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/wordpress-developer-resource-hookr-io-now-with-improved-search?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wordpress-developer-resource-hookr-io-now-with-improved-search\' title=\'Hookr.io, the WordPress developer resource that launched earlier this year has undergone a series of improvements. The search engine now shows results as your typing. The detailed results page has been completely redesigned making it easier to read. If the source code contains indexed objects such as actions, filters, functions, etc, those items are hyper-li\'>WPTavern: WordPress Developer Resource Hookr.io Now With Improved Search</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/preview-the-wordpress-menu-customizer-alpha-plugin-ready-for-testing?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=preview-the-wordpress-menu-customizer-alpha-plugin-ready-for-testing\' title=\'WordPress 3.9 made huge strides toward improving the theme customization experience by adding widgets to the customizer for live previews. But have you ever thought about the possibility of setting up your WordPress menus within the customizer? Nick Halsey is tackling this as part of his Google Summer of Code 2014 Project and has just released an alpha plugi\'>WPTavern: Preview the WordPress Menu Customizer: Alpha Plugin Ready for Testing</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2014/06/17/designer-discussion-making-the-best-use-of-wordpress/\' title=\'\'>WordPress.tv: Designer Discussion: Making the Best Use of WordPress</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li class=\'dashboard-news-plugin\'><span>Populärt tillägg:</span> <a href=\'http://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration for WordPress</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=edde81a248&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration for WordPress\'>Installera</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),
